{"tid":2236004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反國安法街站遇襲　區議員劉家衡秘書遭控打鬥　准保釋候訊","createTime":"2020-10-09T06:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T08:14:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa3db90978de81f6bca079ba5a301fc51b7f0a7","tid":2236004,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"公民黨區議員劉家衡今年 5 月，在深水埗擺設反國安法街站時，一名中年男子涉嫌襲擊其助理。警方及後拘捕該男子及劉家衡的秘書，控告二人在公眾地方打鬥罪，並加控男子一項普通襲擊罪，二人今（9日）在西九龍裁判法院應訊。案件押後至 11 月 6 日再訊，以待控方索取法律意見，二人均獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%97%E7%AB%99%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%89%E5%AE%B6%E8%A1%A1%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%A7%E6%89%93%E9%AC%A5-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A1%2597%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25AC%25A5-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYznWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=50edcdd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A1%2597%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25AC%25A5-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=6c84d86f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%97%E7%AB%99%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E